WEBVTT

00:05.735 --> 00:16.329
And they say that the most difficult problem on 
Kennedy's desk was, where shall the next

00:05.735 --> 00:16.329
cyclotron go?

00:19.173 --> 00:27.024
Well, you know what happened in November of 63 in 
Dallas? And Mr. Johnson became president as a

00:28.946 --> 00:33.092
consequence of that.

00:37.814 --> 00:45.306
I recall at that time reading an article in the 
journal Science. I've forgotten the author. I

00:49.072 --> 00:50.254
want to say David. It

00:50.274 --> 00:55.402
escapes me. It was entitled, When Pure Science 
Meets Pure Politics. And it was telling the story

01:02.474 --> 01:04.497
of The machinations going on about where shall the 
next cyclotron go?

