events on campus, sometimes not only keeping up

28:36.421 --> 28:51.816
with them, but out there in front pulling them 
along. He was also traveling. You can't imagine

28:54.859 --> 28:59.343
the travels that he took. I think he responded to 
every request made of him to make a speech

28:59.363 --> 29:04.588
anywhere. Whatever the subject so long as it 
related to Texas A&M University. Who were his key

29:11.480 --> 29:14.886
contacts in Austin and Washington? The 
individuals that he knew best that really helped

29:16.708 --> 29:20.775
A&M a lot.

