Tiger Teague in Washington, plus later LBJ 
himself.

29:39.247 --> 29:40.088
Let's see. John Connolly? Yes, John Connolly.

29:51.138 --> 29:55.842
Bill Moore, of course, although he was not in 
Austin, he was of Austin in a way.

30:00.126 --> 30:02.068
Who was Speaker of the House at that time?

30:05.912 --> 30:06.452
I don't know. I don't recall either, but I think 
that was a good relationship for A&M. And was

30:12.787 --> 30:17.433
Heatley one of Mr. Rutter's close contacts? I 
don't recall. As chairman of whatever it was, Ways

30:18.495 --> 30:22.920
and Means or Appropriations? I don't think he was a 
great friend, as I recall. And Senator Aiken? I

30:29.389 --> 30:29.850
don't know. I just don't know about Aiken. During 
the Rutter years, who was the key A&M person to work

30:32.673 --> 30:38.121
with the coordinating board?

30:42.468 --> 30:44.250
His vice president, I think. Right, the chief, 
what we now call the provost, vice president of

30:45.032 --> 30:49.358
academic affairs. Yes. When you first, do you 
recall any event, any circumstance under which

