I don't recall when or how that message came. It's 
not clear in my memory when it came. I remember

31:19.618 --> 31:30.793
hearing that after he was hospitalized, shortly 
after he was hospitalized, he was rushed to

31:19.618 --> 31:30.793
surgery. And he had to be taken in a subterranean

31:32.765 --> 31:44.583
channel from one building to another. And it was 
quite

31:46.205 --> 31:59.025
a group there moving along with him. This was in 
Houston. This is in Houston, yes. Let's see. His

32:07.915 --> 32:12.423
surgeon was, who's the guy? It wasn't DeBakey. It 
was,

32:15.809 --> 32:20.237
do you recall? The other top guy. There are two down 
