each of the deans. I know I was called to express my 
views about those that they were examining.

33:35.619 --> 33:35.980
Really? Oh, good. Didn't know that. How 
appropriate were their questions? Very good

33:42.991 --> 33:45.536
questions. Excellent questions. Among the board 
members, who seemed to be the key movers and

33:48.742 --> 33:53.792
shakers at that point?

