I also had heard prior to my going for the interview 
that Jack Williams was being considered.

34:19.673 --> 34:23.458
And my comment to the board was, you need look no 
further. If you can get this man to come back to

34:25.328 --> 34:33.599
Texas, you will have indeed pulled off a great coup 
for this university. Do you know who it was that

34:34.059 --> 34:38.365
originally suggested his name to them? No. You? 
Earl Rudder told Fort Albritton and John Lindsay a

34:39.606 --> 34:48.518
year and a half earlier in response to their 
question, Earl, God help us if it were to happen,

34:49.021 --> 34:55.952
but what should we do if anything ever happened to 
you? Do you have somebody on site? And Mr.

34:59.678 --> 35:03.204
Albritton said that Mr. Rutter said, no, I don't, 
